* daily task
  - go through each account
    - balance is negative and billing has been not ok in 7 days or longer
      - flag standing = 'bad'
    - go through each instance
      - move instance balance into account balance
      - if billing not ok
        - if good account standing
          - send email that this instance will be deleted if billing is not fixed within X days
        - if bad standing
          - delete instance
          - email that the instance has been destroyed
      - if using too much resources, suggest upgrade unless already suggested

* monthly task
  - go through each account
    - use stripe to charge the account balance
    - if success, set account standing to 'good' and balance to 0
    - if failure, remove credit card, send an email asking for billing info
      - if has instances, warn that unpaid instances will be kept alive only 7 days

* do our own log aggregation (loggly fucking slow)
* support ticket system
* pull cadvisor data from influxdb
